file: template/.gitignore
behavior: Excludes Rust build artifacts and per-task context-cache/report directories from version control while allowing generated context files (rollup.ctx, *.ctx, intent.md) to be committed.
edit_notes:
  - Part of a project template; changes here propagate only to newly scaffolded projects, not existing ones.
  - Must keep .context/.cache/ and .context/.reports/ ignored while leaving other .context/* files (rollup.ctx, *.ctx, intent.md) tracked; do not add a blanket .context/ ignore.
functions:
invariants:
  - Generated context files under .context/ (rollup.ctx, *.ctx, intent.md) remain trackable; only .cache/ and .reports/ subpaths are excluded.
external_deps: